**Privacy by Design**:
- **Enterprise tier**: DEFAULT no retention, orgs can opt-in to training
- **Professional tier**: DEFAULT retention, users can opt-out in settings
- **Hobby tier**: MANDATORY retention for training, no opt-out
- **Internal tier**: NO privacy - all code used for training
- Local-first architecture - data stays on device unless opted-in
- Encrypted communication for any network calls
- Users can delete ALL their data with one click (except Hobby tier training data already used)

Privacy violations are fireable offenses. When in doubt, don't collect.

